### Attributes

Attribute   | Type    | Description
------------|---------|------------
boolean     | boolean |
choices     | array   |
updated_at  | date    |
range       | integer |
text        | string  |
video_token | string  |


### Relations

The <code>answer</code> object always has a relation to a <code>question</code> and a <code>candidate</code>

